---
const pageTitle = "About Angelino's";

const identity = {
  firstName: "Guido",
  country: "oily dimension",
  occupation: "dinner of moms",
  hobbies: ["consuming", "lying", "eating eyes"],
};

const skills = ["hiding", "jumping", "watching", "traps", "potion crafting", "taking your mom out to dinner"];

const happy = true;
const finished = false;
const goal = 8;
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{pageTitle}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/about/">About</a>
    <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
    <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
    <h2>... they smell like cabage!</h2>

    <p>They have olive skin and dark hair. Their skin shimmers like ocean waves in the sun. There will be an odor of cabage and earthly soils upon the air.</p>

    <p>This will be a reference on how to overcome and defeat an Angelino.</p>

    <p>Here are a few facts about the Angelino:</p>

    {happy && <p>I am happy to be learning Astro!</p>}

    {finished && <p>I finished this tutorial!</p>}

    {goal === 8 ? <p>My goal is to finish in 8 days.</p> : <p>My goal is not 3 days.</p>}

    <ul>
    <li>There name is {identity.firstName}.</li>
    <li>I live in {identity.country} and I work as a {identity.occupation}.</li>
    {identity.hobbies.length >= 2 &&
        <li>Two of my hobbies are: {identity.hobbies[0]} and {identity.hobbies[1]}</li>
    }
    </ul>
    <p>My skills are:</p>
    <ul>
    {skills.map((skill) => <li>{skill}</li>)}
    </ul>    
	</body>
</html>
